<i>Kelly met the analyst during her little
stay at Holloway Prison.</i>

1015
01:35:15,544 --> 01:35:18,839
<i>His eyes were
a beautiful shade of blue.</i>

1016
01:35:19,048 --> 01:35:21,509
<i>Did Kelly trust the doctor?</i>

1017
01:35:21,717 --> 01:35:24,887
<i>Did she mean it
when she told him she wanted help?</i>

1018
01:35:25,137 --> 01:35:27,098
<i>Even she wasn't sure.</i>

1019
01:35:27,348 --> 01:35:29,892
<i>If things went well,
then she meant it.</i>

1020
01:35:30,142 --> 01:35:31,560
<i>If not, she didn't.</i>

1021
01:35:31,811 --> 01:35:33,562
<i>That way, she'd be protected.</i>

1022
01:35:33,813 --> 01:35:35,773
<i>She remembered the first time
she met Irena...</i>

1023
01:35:36,023 --> 01:35:37,358
<i>at the party in Bloomsbury.</i>

1024
01:35:37,608 --> 01:35:39,652
<i>She felt a deep affinity
for the older woman.</i>

1025
01:35:39,902 --> 01:35:43,030
<i>As if the two of them leaning against
the wall, silently smoking...</i>

1026
01:35:43,280 --> 01:35:45,157
<i>The next time they saw each other...</i>

1027
01:35:45,366 --> 01:35:47,660
<i>only brought
the two women even closer.</i>

1028
01:35:47,910 --> 01:35:50,204
<i>Even as Dr. Green watched them
through the window...</i>

1029
01:35:50,454 --> 01:35:52,623
<i>looking for any sign of conspiracy.</i>

1030
01:35:52,873 --> 01:35:56,127
<i>Kelly found herself opening up,
trusting the older woman...</i>

1031
01:35:56,377 --> 01:35:58,462
<i>revealing things about herself...</i>

1032
01:35:58,712 --> 01:36:01,048
<i>Yes, Kelly thought. She liked Irena.</i>

1033
01:36:01,298 --> 01:36:05,803
<i>She was trustworthy, intelligent,
beautiful, dignified.</i>

1034
01:36:06,053 --> 01:36:10,433
<i>It was a pity
Kelly was going to have to kill her.</i>

1035
01:36:25,364 --> 01:36:27,199
<i>She dressed carefully.</i>

1036
01:36:27,408 --> 01:36:30,911
<i>She liked to be well-dressed
when she killed.</i>

1037
01:36:31,162 --> 01:36:34,874
<i>Killing Irena and telling Dr. Green
she was planning to do</i> it...

1038
01:36:35,124 --> 01:36:38,085
<i>that was the riskiest thing
she could do.</i>

1039
01:36:40,421 --> 01:36:41,964
Come on, Milena.

1040
01:36:46,177 --> 01:36:48,345
Come on, Milena, answer the phone

1041
01:36:50,181 --> 01:36:54,351
<i>It's Michael Glass here. Can you call
me as soon as you get this message?</i>

1042
01:36:55,853 --> 01:36:58,314
<i>As much as Kelly hated her shrink...</i>

1043
01:36:58,564 --> 01:37:01,358
<i>she also loved him.</i>

1044
01:37:01,567 --> 01:37:05,404
<i>She took a last glance at herself
in the mirror.</i>

1045
01:37:05,654 --> 01:37:10,451
<i>Irena deserved a good death.
And Kelly would give it to her.</i>

1046
01:37:10,701 --> 01:37:13,746
<i>Hello, this is Roy Washburn,
please leave a message.</i>

1047
01:37:13,954 --> 01:37:17,333
Roy. It's Michael Glass.
Come as soon as you can.

1048
01:37:17,583 --> 01:37:21,045
Hi

1049
